1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:01,390
[Disclaimer:
All depicted events are fictional

2
00:00:01,420 --> 00:00:02,420
and for entertainment purposes only;
viewer discretion is advised]

3
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:18,560
[Love Upon a Time Series]

4
00:00:19,740 --> 00:00:20,520
There.

5
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:22,190
That's what Rattikarn,
the fortune teller, said.

6
00:00:22,210 --> 00:00:24,120
So this writing refers to
the incident at the hut?

7
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:25,750
Do I enter the woods by the temple

8
00:00:26,150 --> 00:00:27,480
to find the hut?

9
00:00:34,070 --> 00:00:36,760
You came here alone, did you not?

10
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:38,280
Ma Krathuep Rong.

11
00:00:38,850 --> 00:00:40,500
Very well.

12
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:41,660
Do enjoy yourself.

13
00:00:44,950 --> 00:00:45,800
Have a look!

14
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:47,000
Have a look!!

15
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:48,800
Take a good look!!

16
00:00:51,020 --> 00:00:52,560
He wanted me dead!

17
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:00,600
That lord must harbor
deep resentment toward me.

18
00:01:04,190 --> 00:01:06,510
It is certainly not about
some dalliance between him and Klao.

19
00:01:06,860 --> 00:01:07,780
He knows the truth!

20
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,000
Yes, he certainly does.

21
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:13,680
You.

22
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,420
Do not lay a hand on me!!

23
00:01:23,070 --> 00:01:24,360
Calm yourself, Cherd.

24
00:01:26,150 --> 00:01:27,380
If that were truly the case,

25
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:30,680
he would never have let you go.

26
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:33,000
Klao...

27
00:01:34,390 --> 00:01:36,680
He must be piecing together

28
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,700
what happened to him in the past.

29
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,880
So long as he cannot recall the truth,

30
00:01:42,970 --> 00:01:43,780
I believe

31
00:01:45,289 --> 00:01:46,560
you need not involve yourself.

32
00:01:52,340 --> 00:01:54,280
Why wait until his memory returns?

33
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,479
Better to pluck the thorn out

34
00:01:58,860 --> 00:01:59,479
now.

35
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,449
[Love Upon a Time Series]

36
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:24,680
[Love Upon a Time Series]

37
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,540
God! God! God! God!

38
00:03:44,650 --> 00:03:45,430
Gosh!

39
00:03:45,610 --> 00:03:46,460
That scared me!

40
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:50,560
Why does Klao's mission
have to be this hard?!

41
00:03:51,829 --> 00:03:52,360
I think...

42
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,800
by the time I complete it,

43
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,450
I'll probably have died of a heart attack!

44
00:03:56,770 --> 00:03:57,490
Do not die just yet.

45
00:03:59,040 --> 00:03:59,670
Mommy! Mommy!

46
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:01,530
Mommy!

47
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:07,960
Fortune teller?!

48
00:04:10,220 --> 00:04:11,040
How did you get here?!

49
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,400
On foot.

50
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:13,760
I am foraging in the forest

51
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,840
for a ritual.

52
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:17,920
What is it?

53
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:22,950
Come.

54
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:24,700
It is not yet your time to die again.

55
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,640
Follow me.

56
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:31,810
Fortune teller, wait up!

57
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:14,440
What brings you to these woods
at such a late hour?

58
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:18,000
What is it you seek?

59
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:22,120
Is it a pond you are after?

60
00:05:25,790 --> 00:05:26,480
Yes.

61
00:05:27,590 --> 00:05:29,640
It was mentioned in Klao's notes.

62
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,880
It specified the time

63
00:05:32,220 --> 00:05:34,000
and place for a rendezvous:

64
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,520
a hut by a pond,

65
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,480
accessed through a temple entrance.

66
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:46,650
I believe that

67
00:05:46,670 --> 00:05:48,040
if I complete the mission,

68
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,980
I'll get to return to the future.

69
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:55,960
The future, you say?

70
00:05:58,890 --> 00:05:59,600
Yes.

71
00:06:00,570 --> 00:06:02,400
It's 400 years from now.

72
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,920
I've traveled back in time.

73
00:06:08,060 --> 00:06:10,200
However, there's also a version of you
in the future.

74
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:13,200
Her name is Rattikarn,

75
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:15,980
one of the best fortune tellers
in the country.

76
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:17,760
No.

77
00:06:19,740 --> 00:06:20,850
You did not go on a voyage.

78
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:23,270
You are still Klao, the very same man.

79
00:06:23,730 --> 00:06:24,640
You have not gone anywhere.

80
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:27,360
Again, Fortune teller?

81
00:06:27,950 --> 00:06:29,000
I told you

82
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:30,720
I've traveled through time.

83
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:32,060
My name is Nakun.

84
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,760
- It's not...
- You two are identical, are you not?

85
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,920
You are retracing
every single step of his life.

86
00:06:39,909 --> 00:06:41,040
We both like writing notes.

87
00:06:41,650 --> 00:06:43,800
I worked my way to the market,
the one Klao visited.

88
00:06:44,050 --> 00:06:45,100
I got to meet Pim,

89
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,200
- Cherd,
- Klao.

90
00:06:46,350 --> 00:06:47,930
and everyone connected to Klao.

91
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:48,580
Dear Klao.

92
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,880
Where have you been all this time?

93
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,760
I'm touched by Klao's past.

94
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,360
Father!

95
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,520
It's as if it happened to me.

96
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:54,270
Father!

97
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:11,660
Water may be poured from this bowl

98
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,210
to another,

99
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:19,080
but its essence still flows
from the old one.

100
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:29,720
Wrong place and wrong time.

101
00:07:30,610 --> 00:07:31,890
You chose to return here,

102
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,440
as you wished.

103
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:56,840
I

104
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:58,700
pray

105
00:07:59,850 --> 00:08:02,360
to all the sacred beings of this world:

106
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:05,300
may I be granted

107
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,680
the chance to return

108
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,800
and set things right.

109
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:12,920
I solemnly swear to the heavens...

110
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:17,080
I shall cleanse the stain
upon my family's name

111
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:20,200
and protect those I love at all costs.

112
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:31,360
The knot

113
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:32,820
must be untied

114
00:08:33,299 --> 00:08:35,440
by the very hand that bound it.

115
00:08:36,179 --> 00:08:37,659
You have made your solemn prayer.

116
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:40,360
Thus, you must return to fulfill it.

117
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:44,400
Pray with all your heart,

118
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,490
and your prayers shall be answered.

119
00:08:48,210 --> 00:08:48,960
Indeed.

120
00:08:49,990 --> 00:08:51,320
If you wish to return to your world,

121
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,420
simply make a wish with the stone
I bestowed upon you, by sheer force of will.

122
00:09:00,460 --> 00:09:01,770
I'm afraid it's impossible now.

123
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:05,430
I gave it to Kaew.

124
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,320
Good heavens!

125
00:09:07,970 --> 00:09:09,400
If he makes his prayer before you,

126
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:11,000
the stone will become useless.

127
00:09:12,310 --> 00:09:13,760
Make a wish, Kaew.

128
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,800
This is but a rock.

129
00:09:17,350 --> 00:09:19,280
There's no harm in trying, is there?

130
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:22,080
Kaew was so furious with me
that he cursed me,

131
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:24,320
vowing never to look upon me again
even in the next life.

132
00:09:25,830 --> 00:09:26,960
In the present time...

133
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:28,720
No,

134
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,200
in the next life,

135
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,800
the reason Pun is being so cold to Thee

136
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:37,090
is because of this very stone.

137
00:09:38,930 --> 00:09:40,380
Leave! Be gone!

138
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:41,680
Set wrongs aright!

139
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,500
Wait, Fortune teller! No!

140
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,720
Fortune teller!

141
00:09:54,370 --> 00:09:55,080
Phop.

142
00:09:56,770 --> 00:09:58,860
How did I end up here?

143
00:10:12,110 --> 00:10:14,090
You wandered into the forest in your sleep.

144
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:16,920
A servant found you at the break of dawn.

145
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,760
So I carried you back to safety.

146
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:29,280
When you found me,

147
00:10:29,780 --> 00:10:31,280
was I soaked?

148
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:36,280
Soaked?

149
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:40,120
Not at all.

150
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:44,360
So, what I saw was a dream?

151
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,680
But it felt so real.

152
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:49,200
If I really have been reincarnated,

153
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:51,900
this means that Klao and I

154
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:53,840
are the same person.

155
00:11:06,170 --> 00:11:07,460
Are you not

156
00:11:08,830 --> 00:11:10,000
upset with me

157
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:14,840
about what I told you at the rice field?

158
00:11:16,530 --> 00:11:18,360
How could I?

159
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:21,880
Simply knowing that you love me delights me.

160
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:26,000
Whether you wish for me to be your brother

161
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,880
or anything else,

162
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:32,040
it is your presence in my life
that matters most.

163
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,000
I must change my attire

164
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:50,480
and set out on patrol now.

165
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,640
You should go and bathe now.

166
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:56,520
Phop.

167
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:01,400
I...

168
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,080
I am very worried about Kaew.

169
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:08,630
Please allow me to see him.

170
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,440
Go on.

171
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:18,480
You need not ask me.

172
00:12:20,180 --> 00:12:22,120
From now on, wherever you choose to go,

173
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:24,880
I shall never forbid you again.

174
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:37,480
Let him go

175
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,980
and complete the mission.

176
00:12:42,010 --> 00:12:44,200
Let him go so he can get married
and start a family.

177
00:12:59,140 --> 00:13:01,610
Are you sure
you will never speak to Jom again?

178
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,280
I have heard that

179
00:13:11,770 --> 00:13:13,280
you cursed him, is that not so?

180
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:21,920
Kaew.

181
00:13:22,710 --> 00:13:24,280
Your curse

182
00:13:24,940 --> 00:13:26,520
might come true.

183
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:32,880
It would be a blessing, then.

184
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:36,080
At last, this will make him feel.

185
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,360
Is it truly a blessing?

186
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,680
Do you truly wish it to come true,

187
00:13:44,630 --> 00:13:45,560
or...

188
00:13:46,050 --> 00:13:47,560
are you merely being spiteful?

189
00:13:49,780 --> 00:13:53,680
Last night, the Physician stayed
and watched over you all night long.

190
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:56,560
And you spent the entire night weeping.

191
00:14:06,770 --> 00:14:08,200
I have already driven him away,

192
00:14:09,170 --> 00:14:10,600
and I have already grieved as well.

193
00:14:15,820 --> 00:14:17,760
I have just decided to
seek my father's permission

194
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,560
to move and live with
my relatives in Pak Nam Pho.

195
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,320
We cannot go back and alter the past, Klao.

196
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:38,120
Kaew.

197
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:41,080
Cease this spitefulness.

198
00:14:42,620 --> 00:14:44,160
Your curse

199
00:14:45,220 --> 00:14:47,240
may or may not come true in the next life,

200
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,960
but at least

201
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:53,040
there remains a chance for you two
to be together here.

202
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:58,140
Go and reconcile with Jom.

203
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:04,760
Take my words and reflect upon them well.

204
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,760
Chuay, let us go.

205
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:31,680
Do you think the same as I do?

206
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:32,520
I do.

207
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:35,400
You must speak with the Physician.

208
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:36,600
Not about that!

209
00:15:38,560 --> 00:15:40,280
Klao speaks with such clarity and reason,

210
00:15:40,670 --> 00:15:42,480
as if he were never of unsound mind.

211
00:15:45,510 --> 00:15:46,700
As you are not ill,

212
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,720
you should take your leave now, Klao.

213
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:50,720
I wish not to speak of that matter.

214
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:57,240
Oh, Jom!

215
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:59,840
You spent the entire night
waiting for him before his room.

216
00:16:00,030 --> 00:16:01,120
Put in a little more effort.

217
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:04,280
I hear that Kaew is moving to another city.

218
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,410
So, the rumors from the servants

219
00:16:09,580 --> 00:16:10,600
are true after all.

220
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:12,800
Lo and behold...

221
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:14,880
you still do nothing despite that?

222
00:16:15,870 --> 00:16:18,080
You may claim the need to tend to the sick,

223
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,480
yet Kaew suffers
from an ailment of the heart.

224
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:23,440
Do you have no love or concern for him?

225
00:16:26,780 --> 00:16:27,940
It is precisely because I care

226
00:16:28,470 --> 00:16:30,520
that I must compel him to let go.

227
00:16:31,140 --> 00:16:32,440
It is better for us to be apart.

228
00:16:33,700 --> 00:16:34,720
Is that truly so?

229
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:36,920
Those who love each other

230
00:16:37,620 --> 00:16:39,000
must stay and care for one another.

231
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:41,600
Yet for two men to love one another,

232
00:16:41,980 --> 00:16:43,680
it will only bring suffering to them both.

233
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:47,000
It seems you have completely forgotten Roong

234
00:16:47,430 --> 00:16:49,710
and his story with High Lord Boribanpracha.

235
00:17:01,770 --> 00:17:03,520
Hold it together, Roong.

236
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:04,760
Roong.

237
00:17:06,210 --> 00:17:07,160
Physician.

238
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:08,200
Physician!

239
00:17:09,290 --> 00:17:10,290
Physician!!

240
00:17:10,990 --> 00:17:11,880
What has happened?!

241
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,740
How has it come to this?

242
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:15,160
Father discovered the truth.

243
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:17,880
Thus, he was caned until the break of dawn.

244
00:17:18,849 --> 00:17:20,280
Pray help us, Physician.

245
00:17:25,770 --> 00:17:26,730
I beg of you.

246
00:17:31,290 --> 00:17:32,240
The wounds are severe indeed.

247
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:36,680
I had already warned you
never to involve yourself with him again.

248
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:50,680
Never has anyone brought me
such happiness as you have.

249
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:54,540
I cannot endure life without you.

250
00:17:56,830 --> 00:17:58,300
We did no wrong.

251
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:02,520
It is Father who has gone too far.

252
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:07,670
Urgh!

253
00:18:08,530 --> 00:18:09,310
Ow!!

254
00:18:09,360 --> 00:18:10,120
Roong!

255
00:18:10,260 --> 00:18:11,110
Pray, take your leave.

256
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:12,960
Unhand me at once!

257
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:15,000
Roong!

258
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:28,740
Son!

259
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:31,440
Father.

260
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,360
I have told you

261
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:35,380
not to help him, have I not?!

262
00:18:35,860 --> 00:18:37,880
Roong lingers at death's door, Father!

263
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:41,360
Do not harm him! Do not!

264
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:44,980
No!!

265
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,350
Roong!

266
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:50,440
- Roong!
- Dare not address my son in such a manner!

267
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,310
Take him to the manor at once!!

268
00:18:58,560 --> 00:18:59,640
Confine him.

269
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:03,000
Never let him lay eyes upon my son again!

270
00:19:08,740 --> 00:19:09,440
Release me!

271
00:19:09,710 --> 00:19:10,440
Roong!

272
00:19:13,420 --> 00:19:14,080
Roong!

273
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,160
Roong!

274
00:19:30,870 --> 00:19:32,200
However, not until the break of dawn

275
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,520
did Roong pass away.

276
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:38,220
And so, High Lord Boribanpracha
followed him in death.

277
00:19:39,620 --> 00:19:41,640
I do not wish Kaew to suffer the same fate.

278
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,440
But...

279
00:19:43,670 --> 00:19:44,560
that is likely owing to

280
00:19:45,270 --> 00:19:47,560
his father's inability to accept the truth.

281
00:19:49,010 --> 00:19:50,440
However, Kaew's family

282
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:53,110
does not wish for their son to suffer.

283
00:19:54,210 --> 00:19:55,620
Furthermore, it is likely that

284
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:57,520
your parents do not mind.

285
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,880
As a physician,

286
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,400
I must conduct myself as a pillar for others

287
00:20:01,570 --> 00:20:03,240
and remain trustworthy.

288
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:10,720
People will rely on you

289
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:12,720
for your talents and abilities,

290
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:15,080
not on whom you fall for.

291
00:20:15,950 --> 00:20:18,140
It is not wrong at all to be who you are.

292
00:20:19,170 --> 00:20:21,960
In Ayothaya, there is no law
to condemn those who love their own kind.

293
00:20:23,210 --> 00:20:24,640
In the future,

294
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:27,840
Thailand shall be the first country
in Southeast Asia

295
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:30,120
where women may love one another,

296
00:20:30,530 --> 00:20:31,640
and men likewise,

297
00:20:32,050 --> 00:20:34,680
and where they may wed
under the full protection of the law.

298
00:20:38,890 --> 00:20:40,470
I thought you had finally
come to your senses,

299
00:20:41,220 --> 00:20:43,360
yet you remain as deranged as ever.

300
00:20:45,580 --> 00:20:48,240
Even should the future
unfold as you have foretold,

301
00:20:49,420 --> 00:20:51,040
I shall not live long enough to see it.

302
00:20:51,580 --> 00:20:52,720
Then so be it.

303
00:20:54,550 --> 00:20:55,560
But at least,

304
00:20:56,110 --> 00:20:57,400
in his final moment,

305
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,920
even after being caned
to the brink of death,

306
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:04,480
Roong never thought of
leaving the High Lord behind.

307
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:09,080
Why, then, should you abandon Kaew?

308
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:22,710
Make haste and reconcile with him

309
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:25,840
before it is too late, Jom.

310
00:21:47,770 --> 00:21:48,360
Chuay,

311
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:50,770
when will the rower arrive?

312
00:21:54,340 --> 00:21:54,960
Chuay,

313
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:03,440
are you deeply moved by
the tragedy of the High Lord and Roong?

314
00:22:11,690 --> 00:22:12,600
Yes, indeed.

315
00:22:13,460 --> 00:22:16,680
Lovers should never truly be torn apart.

316
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:26,520
What has passed
between you and the Lord, Master?

317
00:22:27,560 --> 00:22:29,840
Neither of you looked well this morning.

318
00:22:31,060 --> 00:22:33,600
Are you truly going to give up on him?

319
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:37,320
You do not find...

320
00:22:38,370 --> 00:22:40,440
the relationship between
Phop and me to be unacceptable?

321
00:22:43,590 --> 00:22:44,720
It is hard to say, Master.

322
00:22:45,760 --> 00:22:47,120
I simply think

323
00:22:47,140 --> 00:22:49,220
it is better for lovers to love
than to hate one another.

324
00:22:50,470 --> 00:22:52,480
And after you knocked
Physician Jom back to his senses,

325
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:55,230
I found you and the Lord

326
00:22:55,250 --> 00:22:56,680
to be no different.

327
00:23:00,570 --> 00:23:02,200
I do not wish history to repeat itself.

328
00:23:05,140 --> 00:23:06,480
History repeats itself?

329
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:15,080
Chuay.

330
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:18,800
Kindly bring me to Phop, will you?

331
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,600
Yes, Master.

332
00:23:23,520 --> 00:23:25,200
The rower shall be here soon.

333
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,120
Your tea is ready, Masters.

334
00:24:03,460 --> 00:24:04,840
Coming all this way to see me,

335
00:24:05,370 --> 00:24:07,480
I suspect you have more on your mind
than a cup of tea.

336
00:24:09,620 --> 00:24:10,310
Indeed.

337
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,100
There is something I...

338
00:24:13,910 --> 00:24:14,910
wish to speak to you about.

339
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:27,050
It concerns

340
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:29,440
my previous disappearance.

341
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:39,480
A-Chai,

342
00:24:40,770 --> 00:24:43,160
I would like to have
the same steamed buns I ordered last time.

343
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:48,280
Understood.

344
00:24:55,290 --> 00:24:57,730
We had a quarrel

345
00:24:58,940 --> 00:24:59,800
over

346
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:01,850
my attempt to hunt down

347
00:25:02,320 --> 00:25:04,600
the one accusing my father.

348
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:08,210
Whosoever is found guilty of bribery,

349
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:10,120
such as the trafficking of opium...

350
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:13,560
Get a hold of yourself, Klao.

351
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:15,080
Cherd is but a commoner.

352
00:25:17,230 --> 00:25:20,400
The reason I had to
get close to Cherd was that...

353
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,990
You are suspicious of him?

354
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,400
But I have already told you not to...

355
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:27,360
My memories have begun to return.

356
00:25:29,230 --> 00:25:31,560
Before I disappeared,

357
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:34,230
Cherd attacked me.

358
00:25:35,670 --> 00:25:37,080
Here are the steamed buns, Masters.

359
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:43,120
That is rather quick.

360
00:25:45,150 --> 00:25:46,280
Uh...

361
00:25:46,410 --> 00:25:47,560
I would like something sweet.

362
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:51,000
Whatever you offer,

363
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:52,360
I shall gladly have it all.

364
00:25:53,280 --> 00:25:54,520
Fetch me some sweets, will you?

365
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,160
The sweets, if you would.

366
00:26:03,840 --> 00:26:04,640
Yes, Master.

367
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:16,270
You must have heard the rumors

368
00:26:16,910 --> 00:26:19,480
about my frequent visits to see a girl
at the House of Pleasure named Pim.

369
00:26:20,830 --> 00:26:22,240
I was there to gather information.

370
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:26,160
I believed

371
00:26:27,030 --> 00:26:28,830
she knew something about

372
00:26:29,530 --> 00:26:30,240
Cherd

373
00:26:31,490 --> 00:26:32,490
and

374
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:35,800
what had happened before my disappearance.

375
00:26:38,770 --> 00:26:40,540
Here it is.

376
00:26:40,610 --> 00:26:42,080
Here.

377
00:26:42,270 --> 00:26:44,680
Master Klao and Lord Phop...

378
00:26:44,730 --> 00:26:45,650
Impeccable timing.

379
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:47,880
I have just finished preparing the sweets.

380
00:26:48,250 --> 00:26:51,590
It is called 'lu dagun,'

381
00:26:51,620 --> 00:26:55,080
a beloved and well-known sweet from China.

382
00:26:55,140 --> 00:26:56,280
It is made from flour,

383
00:26:56,310 --> 00:26:57,720
soybeans, black beans,

384
00:26:57,740 --> 00:27:00,720
sugar, and sweet osmanthus,

385
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:02,440
commonly known as

386
00:27:02,990 --> 00:27:04,720
'guihua.'

387
00:27:05,180 --> 00:27:07,660
It comes from the city of Tianjin,

388
00:27:07,720 --> 00:27:10,920
by the Haihe River,

389
00:27:11,010 --> 00:27:12,170
near...

390
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,090
Master.

391
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:15,280
A-Chai.

392
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:17,400
My thanks to you both

393
00:27:17,420 --> 00:27:19,040
for your kindness,

394
00:27:19,840 --> 00:27:22,080
but pray let us speak in private first.

395
00:27:22,990 --> 00:27:24,540
Oh, absolutely.

396
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:27,030
Why are you standing here?

397
00:27:27,050 --> 00:27:28,580
They have matters to discuss!

398
00:27:29,030 --> 00:27:30,320
Do not just stand there!

399
00:27:30,340 --> 00:27:33,050
My apologies for the trouble
caused by my establishment.

400
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:34,240
Begone! Begone! Begone!

401
00:27:34,280 --> 00:27:36,300
Get back to your work!

402
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:38,820
My apologies for the trouble
caused by my establishment.

403
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:42,480
I, too, must take my leave.

404
00:27:43,020 --> 00:27:43,920
Master!

405
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:50,040
You probably knew
that I suffer from insomnia.

406
00:27:50,080 --> 00:27:50,690
Mm.

407
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:53,320
Pray tell me,

408
00:27:54,320 --> 00:27:57,200
with whom was I

409
00:27:58,280 --> 00:28:00,910
when I had a quarrel here?

410
00:28:01,120 --> 00:28:02,040
Was it Cherd?

411
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:06,400
No, no.

412
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:10,680
You were there to see a certain lady

413
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:13,620
who was accompanied by a Chinese man.

414
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:19,200
You became intoxicated
after a visit to a tavern.

415
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:22,210
Then you recklessly lunged at them.

416
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,000
Pim.

417
00:28:23,360 --> 00:28:25,020
Why must you hide from me?!

418
00:28:25,630 --> 00:28:26,660
I am not hiding from you!

419
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,810
I receive no more guests!

420
00:28:29,530 --> 00:28:30,320
If not,

421
00:28:31,050 --> 00:28:33,240
then tell me, why are you with this man?!

422
00:28:35,110 --> 00:28:36,790
We must speak at once!

423
00:28:38,030 --> 00:28:40,530
Keep away from my woman!

424
00:28:40,830 --> 00:28:42,560
The Chinese man shouted.

425
00:28:43,580 --> 00:28:44,680
Master Klao!

426
00:28:45,430 --> 00:28:46,720
Leave this place at once!!

427
00:28:52,660 --> 00:28:56,960
In the end, I was forced,
against my will, to bid you leave.

428
00:29:01,210 --> 00:29:02,260
My Lord,

429
00:29:02,710 --> 00:29:05,910
I beg you, do not punish me.

430
00:29:06,700 --> 00:29:10,020
I only wished to maintain order
within my establishment.

431
00:29:10,190 --> 00:29:12,440
That is why I have no choice

432
00:29:12,730 --> 00:29:15,010
but to bid him leave.

433
00:29:15,210 --> 00:29:16,210
That is enough, Master.

434
00:29:16,650 --> 00:29:18,600
I have yet to say anything.

435
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:27,010
I must have been too desperate

436
00:29:29,340 --> 00:29:32,110
to learn the truth from Pim
that I allowed my emotions to take hold of me.

437
00:29:36,420 --> 00:29:37,400
But as you can see,

438
00:29:38,300 --> 00:29:40,280
she must have known something surely.

439
00:29:41,620 --> 00:29:43,230
If she did not,
why would she have avoided me?

440
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:48,800
I must pay
the House of Pleasure another visit.

441
00:29:51,510 --> 00:29:53,390
And for what reason do you tell me this?

442
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:56,400
Why not keep it hidden,
as you have always done?

443
00:29:59,900 --> 00:30:01,560
I have come to realize that

444
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:09,400
you are the one person
I trust most in my life.

445
00:30:16,170 --> 00:30:18,370
From now on,
I shall keep nothing hidden from you.

446
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:26,140
If that is the case,

447
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:28,900
I shall help you.

448
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:40,680
But...

449
00:30:41,750 --> 00:30:44,100
if you must visit the House of Pleasure,

450
00:30:46,740 --> 00:30:48,440
would that not taint your honor?

451
00:31:00,950 --> 00:31:02,720
Back in the woods by the temple
during the revel,

452
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:05,680
Cherd appeared to harbor
a deep resentment toward you.

453
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,820
Should he cross paths with you again,

454
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:10,720
he will certainly leave you for dead.

455
00:31:14,430 --> 00:31:16,040
Therefore, this time,

456
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:18,660
Chuay must step in to see to your care.

457
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:20,080
Do go on, Master.

458
00:31:20,260 --> 00:31:21,800
Pim awaits inside.

459
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:25,530
Go on.

460
00:31:27,860 --> 00:31:29,070
And you?

461
00:31:29,090 --> 00:31:30,600
What will you do?

462
00:31:31,080 --> 00:31:33,040
I shall remain in disguise at a distance,

463
00:31:33,420 --> 00:31:35,240
keeping a watchful eye on you,

464
00:31:35,620 --> 00:31:38,160
so that I may come to your aid
the moment you need me.

465
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:40,600
Remain in disguise?

466
00:31:41,430 --> 00:31:42,340
How so?

467
00:31:45,250 --> 00:31:45,920
Here, Master.

468
00:31:49,950 --> 00:31:50,800
Here you go.

469
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:53,920
How very strange.

470
00:31:54,010 --> 00:31:55,830
All at once, you two

471
00:31:55,850 --> 00:31:58,120
grew interested in mounting a play?

472
00:31:58,860 --> 00:32:01,820
I watched Choi during Songkran,

473
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,880
and I feel inclined to have some fun myself.

474
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,200
What of you, Phop?

475
00:32:06,980 --> 00:32:08,360
What ought you to wear for your disguise?

476
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:12,500
Euang, have you any Farangi attire?

477
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:34,760
You need not wear such attire.

478
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,390
There is one

479
00:32:37,490 --> 00:32:38,960
that ought to suit you better.

480
00:32:48,040 --> 00:32:49,680
May I offer you some cloth?

481
00:32:49,710 --> 00:32:51,470
- Would you like some cloth?
- No, thank you. I am not interested.

482
00:32:51,510 --> 00:32:52,150
Would you like one?

483
00:32:52,180 --> 00:32:53,420
I'm sure they're lovely, yes...

484
00:32:53,460 --> 00:32:54,810
This way, sir.

485
00:32:54,840 --> 00:32:55,750
Right this way.

486
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:56,880
They're so lovely...

487
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,380
- This way. Do come in.
- Would you...

488
00:32:58,420 --> 00:32:59,420
This way...

489
00:32:59,540 --> 00:33:01,290
This way.

490
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:09,650
Who would ever suspect that a lord like Phop

491
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:12,230
would be strolling through
the market selling cloth?

492
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:13,700
This proves that

493
00:33:13,730 --> 00:33:15,040
it is a perfect disguise.

494
00:33:17,810 --> 00:33:19,190
Lovely cloth!

495
00:33:29,480 --> 00:33:30,200
Oh?

496
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:31,320
Klao.

497
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,600
Where might you be heading?

498
00:33:34,250 --> 00:33:35,120
None of your business.

499
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:38,340
Masters.

500
00:33:38,390 --> 00:33:40,560
It is best not to quarrel
in the marketplace like this.

501
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:42,830
Pray, come with me instead, will you?

502
00:33:43,230 --> 00:33:44,930
I hate the effeminate like you.

503
00:33:45,820 --> 00:33:46,390
Good heavens!

504
00:33:46,410 --> 00:33:48,080
Why would I waste my time in women's attire?

505
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:51,740
Last night,

506
00:33:52,330 --> 00:33:54,110
I followed you into the woods,

507
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,360
but I fell asleep.

508
00:33:56,650 --> 00:33:58,500
Then Lord Phop found you.

509
00:33:58,730 --> 00:33:59,650
This time,

510
00:33:59,670 --> 00:34:01,170
I shall not let you slip away.

511
00:34:01,190 --> 00:34:01,730
Come!!

512
00:34:01,890 --> 00:34:02,480
I refuse!

513
00:34:02,500 --> 00:34:03,500
- Come.
- Let me go!

514
00:34:03,810 --> 00:34:04,650
Hands off!!

515
00:34:06,150 --> 00:34:07,860
Would you be interested in some cloth?

516
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:10,699
Gorgeous fabric from Persia.

517
00:34:11,340 --> 00:34:12,280
What madness is this?!

518
00:34:13,429 --> 00:34:14,159
Begone from my sight!

519
00:34:14,179 --> 00:34:14,980
I will have none of your cloth!

520
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:16,620
My fabric is of the finest quality.

521
00:34:16,639 --> 00:34:18,320
Pray, take one.

522
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:21,810
Are you a complete nitwit?

523
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:23,840
I said I will have none of it!!

524
00:34:24,179 --> 00:34:25,070
I beg of you.

525
00:34:25,090 --> 00:34:26,810
Pray, take the whole basket.

526
00:34:27,730 --> 00:34:28,670
Now, Klao! Move!

527
00:34:28,699 --> 00:34:29,489
Get it out!

528
00:34:31,010 --> 00:34:32,880
- Hey! Let me out.
- Ah! I must take my leave now. Ah!

529
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:35,110
- They are truly marvelous.
- Release me!

530
00:34:35,760 --> 00:34:36,639
Curses!

531
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:39,679
Out of my way!

532
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:44,239
Truly gorgeous.

533
00:34:45,750 --> 00:34:47,100
This must be exceedingly expensive.

534
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,600
Are you certain you wish to give me this?

535
00:34:53,449 --> 00:34:53,960
Yes.

536
00:34:56,650 --> 00:34:58,250
Do kindly tell me

537
00:35:00,120 --> 00:35:03,040
that Cherd truly has
nothing to do with the opium trade.

538
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:18,700
Pray,

539
00:35:20,250 --> 00:35:21,460
do answer me

540
00:35:22,230 --> 00:35:23,520
before the candles burn out.

541
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:29,820
I have only seen him smoke it.

542
00:35:32,430 --> 00:35:33,640
Whether he sells it as well,

543
00:35:33,820 --> 00:35:35,040
I do not know.

544
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:37,910
If that is so,

545
00:35:39,530 --> 00:35:41,560
why then did you avoid me?

546
00:35:45,170 --> 00:35:46,480
Now I remember.

547
00:35:47,230 --> 00:35:48,480
You once avoided me.

548
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:52,490
We once had a quarrel at the teahouse.

549
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:55,880
If you know nothing of it,

550
00:35:57,340 --> 00:35:58,600
why then did you avoid me?

551
00:36:01,030 --> 00:36:02,640
I have told you all that I know.

552
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:04,800
Time is running short.

553
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:07,800
Return and see me again tomorrow.

554
00:36:30,610 --> 00:36:31,920
I ask for more time.

555
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,800
Pray tell me that

556
00:36:35,770 --> 00:36:37,890
Cherd has dealings in the opium trade.

557
00:36:51,970 --> 00:36:53,320
He might have dealt some.

558
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:55,450
Some?

559
00:36:57,230 --> 00:36:58,490
How much?

560
00:37:00,660 --> 00:37:03,580
His trade is so vast that
he must have a meeting place

561
00:37:04,380 --> 00:37:06,120
or a hidden cache in the woods,

562
00:37:07,370 --> 00:37:08,120
does he not?

563
00:37:15,810 --> 00:37:16,980
I must take my leave.

564
00:37:19,020 --> 00:37:20,280
Should you need to remain here,

565
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:23,420
I shall ask Pit and Puang to take my place.

566
00:37:32,430 --> 00:37:34,040
I wish only to speak with you.

567
00:37:37,050 --> 00:37:40,210
I shall pay extra
to spend the whole night with you.

568
00:37:45,390 --> 00:37:46,120
What say you?

569
00:37:48,370 --> 00:37:50,600
Or is our friendship over in your eyes?

570
00:37:51,300 --> 00:37:53,160
I am quite at a loss.

571
00:37:54,750 --> 00:37:56,160
I must see Cherd after this.

572
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,400
Is there enough liquor, Master?

573
00:38:22,420 --> 00:38:23,980
Would you like something else?

574
00:38:27,180 --> 00:38:28,930
Pray, wait a moment, Master.

575
00:38:28,970 --> 00:38:29,600
Here.

576
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:41,090
Pit, Puang, who is that woman?

577
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:44,920
She is as imposing as Benyakai herself.

578
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:48,720
Do we have a lady of such appearance?

579
00:38:49,390 --> 00:38:50,520
My thoughts exactly, my Lady!

580
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:54,600
She came here with Master Klao.

581
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:55,780
Indeed.

582
00:38:56,370 --> 00:38:58,600
Yet she makes no move
to serve or attend to anyone.

583
00:38:58,870 --> 00:38:59,830
Yes, my Lady.

584
00:39:00,570 --> 00:39:01,720
Even when guests arrived,

585
00:39:02,010 --> 00:39:03,690
she spoke to no one at all!

586
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,240
It is indeed true!

587
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:26,680
Who might you be?

588
00:39:27,660 --> 00:39:29,080
What brings you to this spot?

589
00:39:30,950 --> 00:39:31,520
Well...

590
00:39:32,380 --> 00:39:33,440
- I...
- Sopha!

591
00:39:38,250 --> 00:39:39,400
Where is Pim?

592
00:39:39,970 --> 00:39:40,920
I am to meet her.

593
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:42,040
Uh...

594
00:39:42,620 --> 00:39:44,320
She is currently with a guest.

595
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,360
Pray, wait a moment.

596
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:46,600
A guest or Klao?

597
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:50,280
Huh?!

598
00:39:50,820 --> 00:39:52,200
I have told you

599
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:54,120
never to let him be with her, have I not?

600
00:39:54,410 --> 00:39:55,000
But...

601
00:39:55,150 --> 00:39:57,140
We cannot choose the guests
who seek our services.

602
00:39:57,160 --> 00:39:58,240
I care not.

603
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,520
Good Master,

604
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:05,440
let me be the one to serve you.

605
00:40:29,130 --> 00:40:30,010
Gorgeous

606
00:40:30,770 --> 00:40:31,600
and charming.

607
00:40:34,230 --> 00:40:35,080
My thanks.

608
00:40:36,560 --> 00:40:38,040
Take care of two of my men.

609
00:40:42,910 --> 00:40:44,960
I shall watch you serve them.

610
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:48,130
But Master...

611
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:49,400
You two.

612
00:40:50,410 --> 00:40:51,000
Move.

613
00:40:52,610 --> 00:40:53,360
Move!

614
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:56,080
Now.

615
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,320
Now!

616
00:41:06,660 --> 00:41:07,330
Move.

617
00:41:10,890 --> 00:41:12,160
Fret not, Pim.

618
00:41:13,470 --> 00:41:14,930
Should they trouble you,

619
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:17,710
I shall deal with them.

620
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:19,370
So now, tell me that

621
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:22,610
Cherd has dealings in the trade.

622
00:41:27,890 --> 00:41:29,480
I shall pay you this much,

623
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:31,480
but pray tell me

624
00:41:32,330 --> 00:41:34,540
this is also what I sought

625
00:41:35,270 --> 00:41:37,240
the last night I came to you.

626
00:41:46,980 --> 00:41:48,120
What is the matter, Pim?

627
00:41:49,890 --> 00:41:51,440
Have I said something amiss?

628
00:41:54,950 --> 00:41:56,320
I am heartbroken!

629
00:41:56,770 --> 00:41:58,320
I held dear our bond as friends,

630
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:01,400
yet in the end,

631
00:42:01,950 --> 00:42:03,630
you used your wealth

632
00:42:04,920 --> 00:42:06,360
to purchase my obedience!

633
00:42:07,030 --> 00:42:08,760
I am no more than a piece of property!

634
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:11,780
It is not so.

635
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:15,210
That is not how I see you.

636
00:42:17,030 --> 00:42:18,220
On the night you last came here,

637
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:20,240
you asked me the same question.

638
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:23,120
I already told you I did not know.

639
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:26,210
Cherd is dim-witted.

640
00:42:26,820 --> 00:42:28,700
He lacks the means

641
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:30,400
to be an opium trafficker.

642
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:35,020
Then you disappeared.

643
00:42:39,430 --> 00:42:41,210
I wish to hear no more questions from you.

644
00:42:42,830 --> 00:42:43,800
Even this alone...

645
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:46,920
I feel utterly wretched!

646
00:43:56,720 --> 00:43:57,720
Master...

647
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:00,630
I pray you, contain your temper.

648
00:44:03,080 --> 00:44:05,000
Why must you act thus, young lady?

649
00:44:05,620 --> 00:44:07,730
Why must you sing like a songbird

650
00:44:08,020 --> 00:44:09,760
in the House of Pleasure?

651
00:44:12,130 --> 00:44:13,880
Perhaps you are not one of the ladies here!

652
00:44:14,160 --> 00:44:15,480
Chaluay, let us depart!!

653
00:44:23,620 --> 00:44:25,080
Let her go, Cherd!

654
00:44:26,360 --> 00:44:27,860
That is the lady I seek!

655
00:44:27,900 --> 00:44:29,920
Do you think I am that dim-witted, Klao?

656
00:44:31,960 --> 00:44:33,130
That is your servant, is he not?

657
00:44:35,840 --> 00:44:37,040
Word from your manor

658
00:44:37,460 --> 00:44:40,600
says that you have changed,
as if you were a different person.

659
00:44:41,230 --> 00:44:42,360
Then why...

660
00:44:42,660 --> 00:44:44,480
do you refuse to stop pursuing me?!

661
00:44:47,120 --> 00:44:49,920
What is it that you remember, Klao?

662
00:44:51,030 --> 00:44:52,240
Another quarrel, is it not?!

663
00:44:52,810 --> 00:44:54,360
Cherd! Klao! Stand apart!

664
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,040
Cherd!

665
00:45:01,980 --> 00:45:02,560
Cherd!!

666
00:45:02,910 --> 00:45:03,480
Yes.

667
00:45:04,190 --> 00:45:06,360
Not a day passes without your brawling.

668
00:45:06,760 --> 00:45:08,880
Do not force me to forbid you
from this place forever.

669
00:45:11,520 --> 00:45:12,360
Dear Klao.

670
00:45:12,620 --> 00:45:13,720
Return to your manor at once,

671
00:45:14,060 --> 00:45:15,120
for Lord Phop has concerns.

672
00:45:19,830 --> 00:45:20,840
Come, Chaluay.

673
00:45:31,170 --> 00:45:32,040
Ah!

674
00:45:32,320 --> 00:45:35,630
Must I change this from the House of Pleasure
to the House of Brawling?!

675
00:45:36,050 --> 00:45:36,600
Urgh!

676
00:45:39,650 --> 00:45:40,280
Move!!

677
00:45:53,320 --> 00:45:54,160
Lord Phop?

678
00:46:08,900 --> 00:46:10,840
Good heavens! Lord Phop, Master Klao.

679
00:46:11,190 --> 00:46:12,560
Do you still find that entertaining?

680
00:46:12,580 --> 00:46:13,960
I nearly lost my life back there.

681
00:46:14,390 --> 00:46:15,400
I am sorry.

682
00:46:15,990 --> 00:46:17,000
My...

683
00:46:17,520 --> 00:46:19,680
What would my life be without you?

684
00:46:22,510 --> 00:46:23,640
It grows late.

685
00:46:24,540 --> 00:46:25,600
Have a rest, Chuay.

686
00:46:26,140 --> 00:46:27,560
I shall see to Dear Klao myself.

687
00:46:28,860 --> 00:46:29,520
Yes, my Lord.

688
00:46:51,970 --> 00:46:53,240
What did you learn back there?

689
00:46:59,020 --> 00:47:01,160
Well, not much.

690
00:47:01,610 --> 00:47:03,160
Pim merely said that

691
00:47:04,020 --> 00:47:05,000
Cherd

692
00:47:05,080 --> 00:47:06,960
lacked the means to do such things.

693
00:47:12,120 --> 00:47:13,080
Interesting indeed.

694
00:47:14,280 --> 00:47:17,120
The soldiers once seized
smugglers carrying opium in Sam Khok.

695
00:47:19,420 --> 00:47:21,730
Were there not a great power
behind the scenes,

696
00:47:22,740 --> 00:47:24,430
they would not remain so silent.

697
00:47:32,730 --> 00:47:33,560
I know.

698
00:47:35,390 --> 00:47:37,120
But if we learn more about Cherd,

699
00:47:37,930 --> 00:47:40,360
we may be able to
trace it back to those behind it.

700
00:47:42,460 --> 00:47:43,020
Phop.

701
00:47:44,540 --> 00:47:45,540
Why...

702
00:47:45,990 --> 00:47:47,720
is Cherd so afraid of Lord Harn?

703
00:47:50,290 --> 00:47:52,810
He has often caused trouble in the market

704
00:47:53,300 --> 00:47:55,400
under Lord Harn's jurisdiction.

705
00:47:56,620 --> 00:47:58,510
He has been punished
on more than one occasion.

706
00:47:58,830 --> 00:47:59,690
Do you think

707
00:48:01,480 --> 00:48:03,440
there is something Lord Harn is aware of?

708
00:48:07,420 --> 00:48:08,920
I shall see to it.

709
00:48:17,030 --> 00:48:19,680
High Lord Soontrapinit,
father to Lord Harn,

710
00:48:20,140 --> 00:48:22,880
has punished
many bandits and opium traffickers.

711
00:48:24,860 --> 00:48:26,530
It may be that he knows certain truths.

712
00:48:37,120 --> 00:48:38,520
Why do you gaze upon me so?

713
00:48:40,550 --> 00:48:41,800
I...

714
00:48:42,250 --> 00:48:44,380
Might I have some more?

715
00:48:49,420 --> 00:48:50,760
That is enough, Klao.

716
00:48:51,330 --> 00:48:52,720
Lest the headache return.

717
00:48:54,540 --> 00:48:55,160
But...

718
00:48:55,240 --> 00:48:57,000
you once told me that

719
00:48:57,570 --> 00:48:58,680
palm wine

720
00:48:58,780 --> 00:49:00,160
does not cause headaches.

721
00:49:00,550 --> 00:49:01,440
Or am I mistaken?

722
00:49:20,220 --> 00:49:23,320
Kindly pour me another, my Phop.

723
00:49:47,150 --> 00:49:48,360
One last pour,

724
00:49:51,420 --> 00:49:52,620
then to sleep.

725
00:50:16,220 --> 00:50:17,440
You have had enough, Klao.

726
00:50:18,120 --> 00:50:19,880
I shall pour you no more,
no matter your pleas.

727
00:50:22,220 --> 00:50:23,120
No.

728
00:50:24,450 --> 00:50:26,010
I am but delighted

729
00:50:26,730 --> 00:50:27,400
that...

730
00:50:30,420 --> 00:50:32,880
I am no longer the only one trying.

731
00:50:40,700 --> 00:50:43,040
Klao, I wish to remain by your side

732
00:50:45,150 --> 00:50:47,400
to support and care for you in all things.

733
00:50:50,740 --> 00:50:53,080
Pray, allow me to look after you.

734
00:51:20,960 --> 00:51:21,800
My Lady!

735
00:51:21,910 --> 00:51:22,480
Hm?

736
00:51:23,040 --> 00:51:23,920
This way!

737
00:51:26,240 --> 00:51:27,040
Oh!

738
00:51:30,100 --> 00:51:30,680
Oh, dear me!

739
00:51:34,970 --> 00:51:37,200
One last pour before bedtime,

740
00:51:37,760 --> 00:51:38,880
so you said.

741
00:51:39,770 --> 00:51:40,640
I must go now.

742
00:51:44,130 --> 00:51:45,440
My Lady, do crouch down...

743
00:51:54,130 --> 00:51:57,600
His Excellency and High Lord must depart
upon an official mission in a few days.

744
00:51:59,370 --> 00:52:02,240
All that Phop utters
is that he is not ready.

745
00:52:03,510 --> 00:52:06,400
To what end must he continue
to put the High Lord off concerning Lady Varna?

746
00:52:08,210 --> 00:52:09,840
Is it true, my Lady?

747
00:52:10,430 --> 00:52:14,220
Is it not because
he already has his heart set on someone else?

748
00:52:16,960 --> 00:52:19,040
Whom would he seek?

749
00:52:19,080 --> 00:52:20,680
His days are consumed by his labors,

750
00:52:20,800 --> 00:52:22,840
and he spends
the whole of his day with Klao.

751
00:52:26,020 --> 00:52:28,320
He seems wholly focused on
tutoring his brother

752
00:52:28,660 --> 00:52:31,440
in preparation for
the civil service examinations.

753
00:52:31,760 --> 00:52:32,700
Oh!

754
00:52:32,990 --> 00:52:35,150
Will he truly be granted the position?

755
00:52:35,410 --> 00:52:37,160
Not once have I beheld Klao at his books.

756
00:52:37,340 --> 00:52:38,920
He prefers to squander his time playing.

757
00:52:39,480 --> 00:52:40,480
Just the other day,

758
00:52:40,950 --> 00:52:43,660
he took your clothes to dress up for a play,

759
00:52:43,950 --> 00:52:44,800
did he not?

760
00:52:45,640 --> 00:52:47,080
Yes, indeed, you are correct.

761
00:52:47,510 --> 00:52:50,520
He even dressed himself as a woman!

762
00:52:53,860 --> 00:52:56,040
Perhaps Klao

763
00:52:56,290 --> 00:52:57,780
- is...
- He is...

764
00:52:59,710 --> 00:53:01,920
Cease this at once, Bud and Euang!

765
00:53:03,220 --> 00:53:05,280
I am seated right here, for heaven's sake.

766
00:53:23,440 --> 00:53:25,000
I swear upon my very life.

767
00:53:25,230 --> 00:53:28,160
Lady Bud and Euang
have already reported the matter to our Lady.

768
00:53:31,750 --> 00:53:34,680
What will become of us, Phop?

769
00:53:35,550 --> 00:53:36,970
Other than Aunt,

770
00:53:38,100 --> 00:53:39,640
there is no one glad to see me.

771
00:53:41,570 --> 00:53:42,960
We shall continue as we are.

772
00:53:44,690 --> 00:53:46,810
Even if I must wed Lady Varna,

773
00:53:47,160 --> 00:53:49,000
I cannot cease loving you.

774
00:53:59,040 --> 00:54:02,200
Aunt Bud has been envious of you
from the very moment you arrived here,

775
00:54:03,670 --> 00:54:05,900
for my parents love and adore you

776
00:54:05,920 --> 00:54:08,960
more than Boon, her own son.

777
00:54:10,420 --> 00:54:11,630
As for Lady Euang...

778
00:54:12,170 --> 00:54:13,920
She knows her child is but a daughter

779
00:54:14,420 --> 00:54:16,720
and will never have the same opportunities
to succeed as you, Boon,

780
00:54:17,060 --> 00:54:18,120
or I.

781
00:54:19,030 --> 00:54:20,840
Thus, all she can do is fawn upon Lady Bud,

782
00:54:21,620 --> 00:54:23,040
seeking her company merely to survive.

783
00:54:29,280 --> 00:54:30,480
Fret not,

784
00:54:31,690 --> 00:54:33,840
for they still bear great respect
for Mother,

785
00:54:36,490 --> 00:54:38,760
and she loves me more than anything else.

786
00:54:39,850 --> 00:54:42,560
It is certain that she, too,
will come to love whom I love.

787
00:54:46,650 --> 00:54:48,700
I fear it will not be so simple, Phop.

788
00:54:49,590 --> 00:54:50,900
Nothing comes effortlessly.

789
00:54:52,220 --> 00:54:55,300
Even my parents did not come to love
one another so easily.

790
00:54:56,220 --> 00:54:57,330
You are aware of that.

791
00:54:59,050 --> 00:55:01,200
Simply speak your heart's desire,

792
00:55:02,050 --> 00:55:04,640
and I will see to it that it comes to pass.

793
00:55:19,300 --> 00:55:20,350
My Lord!

794
00:55:25,120 --> 00:55:26,960
Your subordinate Kla reported that

795
00:55:27,190 --> 00:55:29,610
the patrol unit had seized
sufficient opium to fill an entire cart.

796
00:55:46,080 --> 00:55:48,730
This time, they smuggled it past
Sam Khok and made their way to Thai Ko.

797
00:55:50,030 --> 00:55:51,360
The cart driver slipped away,

798
00:55:52,730 --> 00:55:54,360
but the guards are in pursuit of him.

799
00:55:58,700 --> 00:56:00,440
Will you set it aflame as before?

800
00:56:06,650 --> 00:56:07,640
Confiscate it for now.

801
00:56:08,240 --> 00:56:10,680
Should their associates
in the capital learn of this,

802
00:56:11,660 --> 00:56:12,960
they might come to reclaim it.

803
00:56:17,530 --> 00:56:18,960
Reclaim all of it in one stroke?

804
00:56:20,160 --> 00:56:21,760
Who would dare be so audacious?

805
00:56:22,340 --> 00:56:24,240
We have seized more this time
than ever before.

806
00:56:24,800 --> 00:56:26,200
Its value is immense.

807
00:56:26,830 --> 00:56:28,240
They will not let it go so easily.

808
00:56:29,580 --> 00:56:30,920
Lord Harn, there is a chance

809
00:56:31,260 --> 00:56:33,480
we may trace this back to those behind it.

810
00:56:39,290 --> 00:56:40,760
Upstairs at once.

811
00:56:42,460 --> 00:56:43,040
Now.

812
00:57:03,040 --> 00:57:04,880
Have someone keep close watch over Cherd.

813
00:57:05,210 --> 00:57:06,830
Observe his every move,

814
00:57:07,170 --> 00:57:09,230
and seize him in the act.

815
00:57:09,840 --> 00:57:10,480
Yes, my Lord.

816
00:57:29,180 --> 00:57:31,000
Your end is near, Cherd.

817
00:57:33,080 --> 00:57:33,840
Here it is,

818
00:57:34,050 --> 00:57:34,820
the finest of all.

819
00:57:46,770 --> 00:57:47,460
Master Klao!

820
00:57:51,040 --> 00:57:52,000
Master.

821
00:57:52,710 --> 00:57:53,470
Master Klao.

822
00:57:53,510 --> 00:57:54,840
I beg of you.

823
00:57:55,450 --> 00:57:56,660
The lord has returned to the manor.

824
00:57:56,830 --> 00:57:58,280
We should return as well.

825
00:57:58,820 --> 00:58:01,480
If Lord Phop discovers that
we have been trailing him

826
00:58:01,920 --> 00:58:03,640
and keeping watch until the dead of night,

827
00:58:03,660 --> 00:58:04,920
I shall surely lose my head, Master.

828
00:58:06,420 --> 00:58:07,040
No.

829
00:58:07,680 --> 00:58:09,390
I must see it with my own eyes.

830
00:58:10,370 --> 00:58:12,360
In my time, when such things occurred,

831
00:58:12,740 --> 00:58:15,000
the patrol was but powerless to act!

832
00:58:16,490 --> 00:58:17,400
Master Klao!

833
00:58:35,790 --> 00:58:36,360
Hey!

834
00:58:44,170 --> 00:58:45,480
Wake up.

835
00:58:59,230 --> 00:59:00,280
It smells of burnt beans.

836
00:59:01,540 --> 00:59:02,270
Are they castor beans?

837
00:59:04,660 --> 00:59:06,000
These people have been poisoned.

838
00:59:09,600 --> 00:59:10,700
Muan once told me that

839
00:59:10,720 --> 00:59:12,360
castor beans are exceedingly poisonous.

840
00:59:12,660 --> 00:59:14,040
How did you know of this?

841
00:59:19,790 --> 00:59:21,480
Because the truth remains but one.

842
00:59:23,060 --> 00:59:25,160
I am Detective Conan.

843
00:59:31,450 --> 00:59:31,930
Hey!

844
00:59:32,020 --> 00:59:32,560
Hey!

845
01:00:26,020 --> 01:00:26,760
Hey!

846
01:00:29,810 --> 01:00:30,520
Master!

847
01:01:22,860 --> 01:01:23,540
Phop!

848
01:02:15,170 --> 01:02:16,200
The bandits...

849
01:02:17,540 --> 01:02:19,340
They did not even search through the piles.

850
01:02:21,730 --> 01:02:24,130
They could get hold of the key
and unlock the door with ease.

851
01:02:26,410 --> 01:02:27,220
On top of that...

852
01:02:28,980 --> 01:02:30,840
they could drug the guards

853
01:02:31,320 --> 01:02:32,200
without their

854
01:02:32,730 --> 01:02:33,960
ever noticing.

855
01:02:39,790 --> 01:02:40,440
Phop.

856
01:02:41,540 --> 01:02:42,520
I believe that...

857
01:02:44,010 --> 01:02:45,420
the culprit

858
01:02:47,420 --> 01:02:48,840
is likely from your own

859
01:02:49,440 --> 01:02:50,720
Patrol Department.

860
01:02:57,080 --> 01:02:57,720
Oh.

861
01:02:59,200 --> 01:03:00,040
Is that so?

862
01:03:18,380 --> 01:03:19,140
Phop.

863
01:03:22,540 --> 01:03:24,400
The one whose arm you cut…

864
01:03:26,050 --> 01:03:27,770
his cry

865
01:03:27,800 --> 01:03:28,840
was similar to Cherd's.

866
01:03:36,530 --> 01:03:37,360
It is unlikely to be him.

867
01:03:38,590 --> 01:03:40,900
I had my subordinate Kla watch over him.

868
01:03:42,600 --> 01:03:44,030
He reported that

869
01:03:46,000 --> 01:03:48,110
Cherd had been at Thong's tavern

870
01:03:48,690 --> 01:03:50,040
since dusk.

871
01:03:50,420 --> 01:03:52,800
Only when the matter was over
did he return to his manor.

872
01:04:01,670 --> 01:04:04,160
You may scold or chastise me as you will.

873
01:04:20,120 --> 01:04:21,900
Your heart is already heavy with guilt.

874
01:04:23,920 --> 01:04:26,110
To scold you further
would only cause you more pain.

875
01:05:11,000 --> 01:05:13,540
I am more than relieved
that you made it out alive.

876
01:05:17,040 --> 01:05:18,080
I beg you, listen to me.

877
01:05:19,670 --> 01:05:21,000
This is not an order,

878
01:05:22,800 --> 01:05:23,980
but a humble plea.

879
01:05:26,150 --> 01:05:27,910
Whatever you do,

880
01:05:28,540 --> 01:05:29,610
or wherever you go,

881
01:05:31,620 --> 01:05:33,880
keep me in your heart
a little more than before.

882
01:05:35,840 --> 01:05:37,620
Should any harm befall you,

883
01:05:39,780 --> 01:05:42,200
I would surely perish
of a broken heart thereafter.

884
01:05:48,210 --> 01:05:49,320
I apologize.

885
01:05:51,230 --> 01:05:52,180
From now on,

886
01:05:53,020 --> 01:05:54,860
even when I go to the privy,

887
01:05:55,260 --> 01:05:56,640
I shall let you know.

888
01:05:58,770 --> 01:05:59,360
Pray...

889
01:06:00,310 --> 01:06:01,720
cease being upset with me, will you?

890
01:06:07,380 --> 01:06:08,440
Why this laughter?

891
01:06:09,340 --> 01:06:10,640
I am serious.

892
01:06:12,700 --> 01:06:13,640
Cute.

893
01:06:15,230 --> 01:06:16,900
A stubborn soul such as yours,

894
01:06:17,830 --> 01:06:19,640
yet acting so sweet and clingy,

895
01:06:20,820 --> 01:06:22,400
is truly charming.

896
01:06:27,620 --> 01:06:28,240
I...

897
01:06:28,420 --> 01:06:29,550
I am truly sad at present.

898
01:06:33,180 --> 01:06:34,320
You no longer are, it seems,

899
01:06:35,430 --> 01:06:36,430
for you can now smile again.

900
01:06:58,350 --> 01:06:59,010
Klao...

901
01:07:03,850 --> 01:07:06,960
I know that many hardships lie before us,

902
01:07:10,370 --> 01:07:11,740
yet I promise

903
01:07:12,980 --> 01:07:14,990
to protect you with all my might.

904
01:07:27,020 --> 01:07:28,640
Let me care for you

905
01:07:29,520 --> 01:07:32,080
until my very last breath.

906
01:07:36,060 --> 01:07:38,310
Could you find it in your heart
to accept my love?

907
01:07:58,520 --> 01:07:59,880
Have I made myself clear?

908
01:09:45,529 --> 01:09:47,020
If you do not stop me now,

909
01:09:49,830 --> 01:09:51,760
I shall follow my heart's desire.

910
01:09:53,830 --> 01:09:55,480
Why should I stop you,

911
01:09:58,660 --> 01:10:00,930
when I, too,
am following my heart's desire?

912
01:11:33,590 --> 01:11:34,800
Fret not,

913
01:11:36,120 --> 01:11:37,760
for I shall treat you
with the utmost tenderness.

914
01:12:13,030 --> 01:12:14,360
Does it feel pleasant to you?

915
01:13:35,790 --> 01:13:42,340
♫Only you I want to see,
no matter how many lifetimes pass♫

916
01:13:42,560 --> 01:13:43,960
I love you dearly.

917
01:13:56,660 --> 01:13:58,840
I also love you dearly, alright?

918
01:14:00,270 --> 01:14:00,910
Alright.

919
01:14:26,660 --> 01:14:28,760
I have prepared
this meal for you today, you see.

920
01:14:29,000 --> 01:14:30,810
Do you often bring me meals like this?

921
01:14:30,840 --> 01:14:31,720
Not at all, Master.

922
01:14:31,800 --> 01:14:33,740
It is his usual practice
to prepare it for the Physician each day.

923
01:14:33,760 --> 01:14:34,640
Buaphan!

924
01:14:34,960 --> 01:14:37,040
Have I not told you
to speak of him no more?

925
01:14:39,600 --> 01:14:40,500
While I am away,

926
01:14:40,830 --> 01:14:43,240
keep close watch over the servants.

927
01:14:43,460 --> 01:14:44,520
Yes, my Lady.

928
01:14:44,580 --> 01:14:47,800
I shall keep watch
to ensure nothing disgraceful occurs.

929
01:14:48,790 --> 01:14:49,920
I... I promise that

930
01:14:50,240 --> 01:14:51,840
from now on, it shall never happen again.

931
01:14:51,880 --> 01:14:53,840
There shall certainly
be no such incident again,

932
01:14:54,040 --> 01:14:55,080
for you

933
01:14:55,300 --> 01:14:57,700
shall no longer remain in my household!

934
01:14:57,720 --> 01:14:58,440
Father!

935
01:14:59,210 --> 01:15:00,320
What is amiss, Phop?

936
01:15:01,100 --> 01:15:02,480
I love him

937
01:15:02,910 --> 01:15:04,590
as one would love one's beloved, Father.

938
01:15:17,190 --> 01:15:24,370
♫Only you I want to see,
no matter how many lifetimes pass♫

939
01:15:24,660 --> 01:15:28,570
♫I'll plead to the stars so that we'll meet again♫

940
01:15:28,600 --> 01:15:32,320
♫I wish to fall in love with you
until the very end♫

941
01:15:32,360 --> 01:15:36,080
♫We'll meet again,
no matter how many lifetimes pass♫

942
01:15:36,120 --> 01:15:39,890
♫It's all yours alone, my beating heart♫

943
01:15:39,940 --> 01:15:43,670
♫May fate guide our paths♫

944
01:15:43,740 --> 01:15:47,220
♫And reunite us through dawns and dusks♫

945
01:15:47,240 --> 01:15:51,420
♫My heart is all yours♫

946
01:16:01,840 --> 01:16:05,800
[Love Upon a Time Series]
